  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
<list>
<item>Solve problems involving heat transfer to and from ideal monatomic gases whose volumes are held constant</item>
<item>Solve similar problems for non-monatomic ideal gases based on the number of degrees of freedom of a molecule</item>
<item>Estimate the heat capacities of metals using a model based on degrees of freedom</item></list></md:abstract>
